title: Baby Daddy Season 1 - 2 - 3
description: Baby Daddy is an ABC Family original comedy television series that premiered on June 20, 2012.The series follows Ben, a guy in his twenties, who gets the surprise of his life when a one night stand leaves her baby at his doorstep. Ben decides to raise his little girl with the help of his brother, Danny, his two close friends, Riley and Tucker, and his mother, Bonnie.
